{"tid":2462094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳女皇不願登基近70年始與家人鬧翻 哈里專訪丈夫入院令壓力倍增","createTime":"2021-03-25T19:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T22:35:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"38d5607b97ab546255b5c5732d89bf6a2a3a9108","tid":2462094,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:26:09.000Z","msg":"英國哈里王子及妻子梅根早前接受美國名嘴奧花雲費專訪，導致皇室一家關係變得更緊張。有消息人士透露，女皇在專訪播出時還要面對丈夫菲臘親王入院，就像一切都落在她的肩膀上，她也不希望臨近明年登基70年才跟家人鬧翻。<br />\n<br />\n英女皇伊利沙伯二世將在明年2月6日慶祝登基70年。英國《每日快報》引述消息人士指，女皇「不想皇位坐到這階段時，出現家庭爭吵」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210326/VG74OUVGGVCIFEAZUQ5HOYDJXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210326%2FVG74OUVGGVCIFEAZUQ5HOYDJXM%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=b281d326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210326%2FVG74OUVGGVCIFEAZUQ5HOYDJXM%2F&h=4ec34376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210326/VG74OUVGGVCIFEAZUQ5HOYDJXM/</a>"},{"pid":"673ddef44f242a6e3046f2f237301431eab2ad0c","tid":2462094,"uid":261699,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:38:09.000Z","msg":"乜鳩嘢標題嚟&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ef94762e132338ac05072ef9fa3223aaf66869a4","tid":2462094,"uid":108837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"673ddef44f242a6e3046f2f237301431eab2ad0c","tid":2462094,"uid":261699,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:38:09.000Z","msg":"乜鳩嘢標題嚟&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:42:31.000Z","msg":"仲衰過兒子生性病母感安慰"},{"pid":"a722b9068a9f101c1a962d9c15f3e66c9b8466c8","tid":2462094,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef94762e132338ac05072ef9fa3223aaf66869a4","tid":2462094,"uid":108837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"673ddef44f242a6e3046f2f237301431eab2ad0c","tid":2462094,"uid":